{"tid":862808,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"在一間韓國公司上班，你問我答","createTime":"2018-10-15T06:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T17:33:31.000Z","uid":129825,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"90eae660a598efa5d92e934f377aa7c1f4a39503","tid":862808,"uid":129825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T06:29:54.000Z","msg":"做左兩年，每日都有新鮮事，每日都咁歡樂。<br />\n啲oba真係好識搞gag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606bb38a9a0b58e09fa99f1366527aa233ac1188","tid":862808,"uid":193613,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T06:36:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母 關我撚事</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f69e5505f5939c6a682cb96b53bcf183cbc9dbd","tid":862808,"uid":129825,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T06:37:25.000Z","msg":"現時個個港男都鐘意扮偽韓仔，女既鐘意煲韓劇，你敢話唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87079b4addb950622efad8c781d570d8b616135","tid":862808,"uid":26018,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T06:48:55.000Z","msg":"我都想做接待處女小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c798b0a11663debeac5530428d96119ff18333c3","tid":862808,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T06:51:21.000Z","msg":"啲女點"},{"pid":"4bb1bb1b1d7ffde3881072d07b4d49f5121a159e","tid":862808,"uid":129825,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T06:53:27.000Z","msg":"韓國人，是一個很尊重輩份的民族。<br />\n<br />\n先不論公司架構，就算你是一個manager, 當年老的司機請你幫手落貨，你也要幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n就一韓國間建築公司為例， 韓國公司是從不聘請專家的，他們崇尚全能的下屬。<br />\n一個約50-60人的部門，職位最高的人是project director/managing director。<br />\n而下線被分開為planning, technical及operation team。<br />\n每個小分部都有一位課長，與日本的會社體制相約。<br />\n<br />\n就韓國人而言，於公司經驗是遠遠比知識及技術更為重要。一個待在公司40年的老臣子遠比一個工作了10年的注冊surveyor重要。<br />\n<br />\n作為一個畢業生，你要對於韓國上司的期望有所覺悟。<br />\n日常的私人事務，例如：打掃家居衛生，為他準備洗衣服務，週末的golf booking, 你必須隨傳隨到。<br />\n<br />\n而工作方面，你要打醒12精神，一個從業員必須要有3個人的工作效率。"},{"pid":"cfd1a1702544a7765c9b71d1a9775a786cdf6c33","tid":862808,"uid":129825,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"c798b0a11663debeac5530428d96119ff18333c3","tid":862808,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T06:51:21.000Z","msg":"啲女點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T07:03:10.000Z","msg":"無乜特別，一般都好有禮貌，入門口已經低頭點點頭，保持笑容。  工作上十分盡責，對比韓國男性更為可靠。<br />\n<br />\n外表方面：<br />\n韓國女性就係眼細，面粗 只係我地對佢地既傳統幻想。<br />\n其實好多韓國女性都係大眼。<br />\n<br />\n衣著方面，如果唔係經常留於office既職員，其實都係smart casual為主。 而officer一般都要穿上公司制服（風嬲）<br />\n<br />\n30歲打後既韓國女性偏向僕素，唔太會化濃妝。除左要經常見老闆既accountant姐姐。<br />\n<br />\n20幾歲既年輕韓國女性有別於傳統思想，佢地遇到上司只會微微點頭，而唔會太誇張。"},{"pid":"e73bbaa416d93a84da72ed1115268aa29847d35e","tid":862808,"uid":31290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:11:39.000Z","msg":"點入行<br />\n你本身識韓文？"},{"pid":"dd4ec513a73a39668c95bcc2e6e687d96d6775ea","tid":862808,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T14:07:53.000Z","msg":"想娶韓妹...有無介紹?唔好過25就得"},{"pid":"96e2929a1079237ce82b0932e2c15f8596f921b7","tid":862808,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f69e5505f5939c6a682cb96b53bcf183cbc9dbd","tid":862808,"uid":129825,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T06:37:25.000Z","msg":"現時個個港男都鐘意扮偽韓仔，女既鐘意煲韓劇，你敢話唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T14:14:55.000Z","msg":"人在日本 sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0517d6dadbe11374bead70ead3f8b59008e0dbd4","tid":862808,"uid":193524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T14:17:18.000Z","msg":"清潔姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43296bb596311605a8eeb146791fb83a414c10b9","tid":862808,"uid":16968,"like